These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, country, disco, funk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, pall-mall, alhambra, tiparillo
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, rugby, sailing
1. the tiparillo-smoker is the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the alhambra-smoker is not the fan of classical##6
5. the person who's sport is rugby is not the tiparillo-smoker##6
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
7. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere between the fan of disco and the pall-mall-smoker##7
8. the person who's sport is badminton is between the fan of country and the fan of disco##2
9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | funk      | country   | classical  |
| Cigar   | tiparillo    | alhambra   | ritmeester | pall-mall  |
| Sport         | sailing | badminton | rugby     | ice-hockey |

