.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, cauliflower, pepper, raspberry
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, airplane, snowmobile, bus
 1. the person eating raspberry is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
 3. the person drinking sprite is not the person eating cauliflower##6
 4. the person drinking water is the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person eating blueberry is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the person eating pepper is the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 9. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person eating raspberry and the person drinking sprite##7
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up         | sprite    | water  |
| Food          | raspberry     | cauliflower | blueberry | pepper |
| Transport   | trike     | airplane     | snowmobile  | bus |

