3. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
4. the manager is somewhere between the fan of country and the journalist##7
5. the journalist is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the mouse is the paramedic##1
8. the fan of blues is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
