3. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the fan of electronic##5
4. the fan of pop is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan of electronic##1
6. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the fan of indie##5
8. the fan of pop is not the british##6

.:: Answer ::.
