4. the person driving the boat is not the person eating spinach##6
5. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
6. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person driving the snowmobile##7
