.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, r&b, rock
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indonesian, mexican, nigerian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, begonia, rose, orchid
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5
4. the fan of d&b is between the indonesian and the person who growsorchid##2
5. the nigerian is not the fan of r&b##6
6. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
7. the person who growsorchid is the mexican##1
8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
9. the nigerian is somewhere between the person who growsbegonia and the fan of blues##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | d&b        | r&b        | rock   |
| Nationality   | mexican | nigerian   | indonesian | french |
| Flower           | orchid  | rose | begonia       | marigold |

