 4. the fan of metal is between the canadian and the egyptian##2
 5. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
 6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 7. the canadian is not the person drinking fanta##6
 8. the fan of d&b is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 9. the american is somewhere to the left of the egyptian##5
10. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
11. the american is between the egyptian and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
